march price fell in german state on year-ago the cost of live in north rhine-westphalia , germani 's most popul state , fell 0.1 pct in the month to mid-march to stand 0.5 pct lower than at the same time a year earlier , the region statist offic said . price had risen 0.3 pct in the month to mid-februari but had fallen 0.7 pct year-on-year . the region figur are consid a good guid to nation inflat trend . the feder statist offic is due to publish provision nation figur for march by the end of thi month .